ttps://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kdDJQeDFiTciHxNrBTyKd7-1280-80.png.webp 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kdDJQeDFiTciHxNrBTyKd7-1024-80.png.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kdDJQeDFiTciHxNrBTyKd7-768-80.png.webp 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kdDJQeDFiTciHxNrBTyKd7-415-80.png.webp 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kdDJQeDFiTciHxNrBTyKd7-360-80.png.webp 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kdDJQeDFiTciHxNrBTyKd7-320-80.png.webp 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\"/\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kdDJQeDFiTciHxNrBTyKd7-320-80.png\" alt=\"Collection of shaped baubles on a stool. There is a classic green one, Christmas pudding and sausage dog\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kdDJQeDFiTciHxNrBTyKd7-1920-80.png 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kdDJQeDFiTciHxNrBTyKd7-1600-80.png 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kdDJQeDFiTciHxNrBTyKd7-1280-80.png 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kdDJQeDFiTciHxNrBTyKd7-1024-80.png 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kdDJQeDFiTciHxNrBTyKd7-768-80.png 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kdDJQeDFiTciHxNrBTyKd7-415-80.png 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kdDJQeDFiTciHxNrBTyKd7-360-80.png 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kdDJQeDFiTciHxNrBTyKd7-320-80.png 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\" loading=\"lazy\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kdDJQeDFiTciHxNrBTyKd7.png\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kdDJQeDFiTciHxNrBTyKd7.png\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e(Image credit: M\u0026amp;S)\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eBut there is more to this nostalgic Christmas trend beyond the return of traditional red and green. Why are we loving such nostalgic decor this year?\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e‘Handcrafted decorations not only infuse a rustic charm but also carry stories and individuality,’ says Lena Gierasinska, Head of Product and Displays at \u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://barkerandstonehouse.sjv.io/c/221109/1016293/13315?subId1=idealhome-gb-2399872460099025267\u0026amp;sharedId=idealhome-gb\u0026amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barkerandstonehouse.co.uk%2F\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"sponsored noopener\" data-url=\"https://www.barkerandstonehouse.co.uk/\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\" data-hl-processed=\"hawklinks\" data-placeholder-url=\"https://barkerandstonehouse.sjv.io/c/221109/1016293/13315?subId1=hawk-custom-tracking\u0026amp;sharedId=hawk-prefix\u0026amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barkerandstonehouse.co.uk%2F\" data-google-interstitial=\"false\" data-merchant-name=\"Barker \u0026amp; Stonehouse\" data-merchant-id=\"201665\" data-merchant-url=\"barkerandstonehouse.co.uk\" data-merchant-network=\"ImpactRad\"\u003e\u003cu\u003eBarker \u0026amp; Stonehouse\u003c/u\u003e\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv data-hydrate=\"true\" id=\"slice-container-newsletterForm-articleInbodyContent-vV5m9W5uzyGVjwjoh2b9YQ\"\u003e\u003csection\u003e\u003cp\u003eSign up to our newsletter for style and decor inspiration, house makeovers, project advice and more.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e‘Unlike the sleek, minimalist approach of colour-blocked décor, many are now embracing pieces that tell a story—adding layers of texture, depth, and personality to their homes. It offers a sense of timelessness and authenticity, creating warmth and cosiness in the home.’\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eNostalgic Christmas is easily the most wholesome of all the Christmas trends and M\u0026amp;S has easily nailed it. The jolly reds and kitsch baubles have us itching to put our decorations up. Has anything caught your eye?\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
